  "detailed_description": "RADical ROACH is a fast paced shoot em’ up, set minutes after nuclear hell falls from the sky engulfing all but a few tough little bugs. Play as the super little radiated roach with new found powers, get to safety before the army of fleas gets you.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast paced shmup action.<br></li><li>A cartoony world full of cute but deadly little bugs.<br></li><li>Spit through a huge variety of enemies <br></li><li>Savage boss creatures.<br></li><li>Venture through unique environments.<br></li><li>Controller support.<br></li><li>35 steam achievements..</li></ul>",
